## 🗂️ Repository Structure

```
SpecStoryTDD/
├── src/
│   └── backend/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       ├── api.py          # FastAPI application (REST endpoints)
│       ├── config.py       # pydantic-settings configuration
│       ├── engine.py       # AlignmentEngine — core analysis + retry loop
│       └── models.py       # Pydantic data models (request / response)
├── tests/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── test_engine.py      # Unit tests for AlignmentEngine
│   └── test_api.py         # Integration tests for FastAPI endpoints
├── data/
│   └── samples/
│       ├── user_story_login.md    # Example user story (with intentional conflicts)
│       └── openapi_login.json     # Example OpenAPI spec (with intentional conflicts)
├── docs/
│   └── architecture.md     # Architecture diagrams and component descriptions
├── pyproject.toml          # Project metadata, dependencies, tooling config
└── README.md
```

